    clock_design.text	Clock Manager design
    mem_barrier.text	Memory Barrier notes
    privilege.text	Process Privilege Control
    pwm_design.text	PWM (Pulse Width Modulator) design
    spi0_design.text	rgSpi0 Design architecture
    uspi_design.text	rgUniSpi Design Architecure
    version.text	Version Numbering, Version Log

